results_dir_format:
db_filename: infer-out/results.db
db_schema: 
      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS procedures
        ( proc_uid TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL
        , proc_attributes BLOB NOT NULL
        , cfg BLOB
        , callees BLOB NOT NULL
        )
    ;

      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS source_files
        ( source_file TEXT PRIMARY KEY
        , type_environment BLOB NOT NULL
        , integer_type_widths BLOB
        , procedure_names BLOB NOT NULL
        , freshly_captured INT NOT NULL )
    ;

      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS specs
        ( proc_uid TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL
        , proc_name BLOB NOT NULL
        , report_summary BLOB NOT NULL
        , summary_metadata BLOB
        , AnnotMap BLOB, Biabduction BLOB, BufferOverrunAnalysis BLOB, BufferOverrunChecker BLOB, ConfigImpactAnalysis BLOB, Cost BLOB, DisjunctiveDemo BLOB, LabResourceLeaks BLOB, LithoRequiredProps BLOB, Pulse BLOB, Purity BLOB, Quandary BLOB, RacerD BLOB, ScopeLeakage BLOB, SIOF BLOB, Lineage BLOB, LineageShape BLOB, Starvation BLOB, Nullsafe BLOB, Uninit BLOB
        )
    ;

      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS model_specs
        ( proc_uid TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL
        , proc_name BLOB NOT NULL
        , report_summary BLOB NOT NULL
        , summary_metadata BLOB
        , AnnotMap BLOB, Biabduction BLOB, BufferOverrunAnalysis BLOB, BufferOverrunChecker BLOB, ConfigImpactAnalysis BLOB, Cost BLOB, DisjunctiveDemo BLOB, LabResourceLeaks BLOB, LithoRequiredProps BLOB, Pulse BLOB, Purity BLOB, Quandary BLOB, RacerD BLOB, ScopeLeakage BLOB, SIOF BLOB, Lineage BLOB, LineageShape BLOB, Starvation BLOB, Nullsafe BLOB, Uninit BLOB
        )
    ;

      CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS issue_logs
        ( checker STRING NOT NULL
        , source_file TEXT NOT NULL
        , issue_log BLOB NOT NULL
        , PRIMARY KEY (checker, source_file)
        )
